588
00:38:15.363 --> 00:38:18.116
Let them grieve me
and think me lost to sea.

589
00:38:21.244 --> 00:38:23.203
Unless you betray me.

590
00:38:23.204 --> 00:38:25.372
You ask me to deceive her.
That is betrayal.

591
00:38:25.373 --> 00:38:28.960
I have asked you nothing.
Father. in all my life.

592
00:38:31.129 --> 00:38:32.880
I ask this one thing
of you now.

593
00:38:32.881 --> 00:38:34.631
Rhaena. Rhaena.

594
00:38:34.632 --> 00:38:35.884
Rhaena!

595
00:38:37.927 --> 00:38:38.928
Rhaena!

596
00:38:40.305 --> 00:38:42.390
[Sheepstealer bellowing]

597
00:38:51.065 --> 00:38:53.067
[screeching]

598
00:38:55.403 --> 00:38:57.405
