612
00:40:28.496 --> 00:40:31.915
[growling]
Useless craven coward!

613
00:40:31.916 --> 00:40:34.042
- Cunt!
- [items clattering]

614
00:40:34.043 --> 00:40:36.545
[growling loudly]

615
00:40:36.546 --> 00:40:38.881
Cunt! Cunt!

616
00:40:38.882 --> 00:40:40.841
Cunt!

617
00:40:40.842 --> 00:40:42.176
[sighs]

618
00:40:48.266 --> 00:40:49.559
[sighs]

619
00:40:54.355 --> 00:40:55.523
[sighs]

620
00:40:57.233 --> 00:40:58.735
[sword sheathing]

621
