701
00:46:00.578 --> 00:46:02.079
Slain by your brother Aemond.

702
00:46:03.372 --> 00:46:05.165
Is that what they say?

703
00:46:05.166 --> 00:46:06.833
Mm.

704
00:46:06.834 --> 00:46:07.959
I'll fucking kill him.

705
00:46:07.960 --> 00:46:10.046
- I'll fucking kill her. the s...
- In time.

706
00:46:12.256 --> 00:46:14.841
There's much to be learned
from the chatter in this camp.

707
00:46:14.842 --> 00:46:18.596
Anonymity is a boon for us.

708
00:46:19.347 --> 00:46:23.684
It will ensure that your
eventual resurrection...

709
